    "Third-party applicationThe application works as a front-end part and provides an interface for the users.",
    "Patients have the right to view their EMRs and authorize or deauthorize third-party entities through the application.",
    "In addition, third-party entities may request patients for access to their EMRs through the application.",
    "After examining and evaluating the EMRs they have accessed, they save the results they have obtained in the database through the application.",
